THE long arm of the law has finally caught up with a criminal who had been on the run. The 49-year-old suspect was bust on Tuesday after months of evading the cops. The police had been looking for him in connection with two cases of attempted murder last year and one of rape in &shy;October. Police spokesman Captain Philemon Khorombi said: &ldquo;He pulled out a gun and pointed it at the police officer. Fortunately, the police officer reacted quickly.&rdquo; According to Khorombi, the suspect was shot by the officer and died on the scene.An inquest case has been opened at the Orlando Police Station.